description:
Mackworth is a infinity scarf handwoven with bamboo, merino wool and tencel in vibrant red, warm brown and grey tones. It is incredibly cozy yet lightweight with a beautiful drape. Inspired by the autumn colors on Mackworth Island; a tiny, scenic place across the bay from Portland Maine, it is great for a hike, a long dog walk or quiet rest on the rocky coast to watch seals, gulls and heron's look for their lunch. 

Infinity scarf measures 16"W x 60"L

