Munjoy is handwoven with cotton, tencel and a wool silk blend. It's vibrant navy blue, sandy taupe and smoky grey with a jolt of lollipop red reflect the vibrancy of people living in the East End neighborhood of Portland, Maine for which it was named. Cozy and stylish, you can dress up or dress down any outfit or outerwear with this gently plaid infinity scarf.

Infinity scarf measures 16"W x 60"L

